-7052-a656-f8ca4cd8c08d","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22809,"content":"整体看还可以","createdAt":"2025-10-21T13:32:27"},{"id":"019a0546-6dd1-71d8-a30a-c7236d63de6b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5624,"content":"鸿蒙就是国产安卓吗？","createdAt":"2025-10-21T13:38:13"},{"id":"019a05f0-50e9-7317-9208-f942a78ea8ab","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24615,"content":"我是上有老下有小，我跟老婆各管各的钱，父母跟着一块住，如果我不给家人换手机、不生病、不出去玩的话，我一个月能剩5k吧","createdAt":"2025-10-21T16:43:46"},{"id":"019a05f2-a02b-73f6-a27c-123c3aed760f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22250,"content":"平时家庭开支怎么算  花你的还是老婆的 ？","createdAt":"2025-10-21T16:46:18"},{"id":"019a0994-8412-70f2-b2ba-22332c2be7de","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22024,"content":"不按家庭没法算，因为有孩子，而且我每个月发了工资都会给媳妇转一部分，按家庭的话，月平均能攒1w+，差不多1.5","createdAt":"2025-10-22T09:41:59"},{"id":"019a0e74-d53b-7336-997e-1a1dd9bf553e","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24615,"content":"吃饭的话家里菜肉是父母买，媳妇负责水电暖气费物业费和孩子衣服玩具等，我负责家里米面粮油营养品和大小电器，衣服由我跟媳妇一块承担，看谁想买了。房贷我俩一块还","createdAt":"2025-10-23T08:25:29"},{"id":"019a2f69-c961-72f8-8ee6-94bdd46f2fad","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3346,"content":"我一个月14.3k，我媳妇9.3k，房贷5.4k，车贷1.4k，每个月底发了工资先往卡里存1w，剩下的作为生活费?","createdAt":"2025-10-29T18:00:53"},{"id":"019a32a8-145a-739e-9983-9bd6a5945007","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1039,"content":"5K-8K吧","createdAt":"2025-10-30T09:07:47"},{"id":"019a32a8-4171-715f-97a3-6b518a40de36","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22809,"content":"很强","createdAt":"2025-10-30T09:07:58"},{"id":"019a32a8-9986-72d3-bb55-c2fc3c1c19d9","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22809,"content":"可以了","createdAt":"2025-10-30T09:08:21"}]